```{.r .cell-code}
view(legis)
legis_line <- legis$FULL_TEXT[7] %>%
  str_split("(?<=\\.)\\s*") %>% # specify the end-of-line character(s)
  pluck(1) 
legis_7 <- legis_line %>%
  str_subset("fish")
view(legis_7)
```

```{.r .cell-code}
combined_legis <- legis %>%
  group_by(Legislature) %>%
  summarise(Combined_Text = paste(FULL_TEXT, collapse = " ! "))
lineee <- combined_legis$Combined_Text[1] %>%
  str_split("(?<=\\.)\\s*") %>% # specify the end-of-line character(s)
  pluck(1) 
legis_1 <- lineee %>%
  str_subset("fish")
length(legis_1)
```
